data.description: Located in Kallison Ranch II, this home is ready for a new owner! The kitchen, which is open to adjoining living room, features granite countertops, gas cooking, stainless appliances & tall espresso stained cabinets. Neutral tile expands through all the entertaining areas. Split floorplan w/ private nook to master suite & secondary beds sharing a hall bathroom. Covered back patio overlooks spacious backyard.
